## 4. Integration với existing system

### 4.1 SuperDictionary.ts + B.1 §9 — canonical ladder

v0.1 source primary = `bangfs_delta_20260420.canonical §III` + `thienbang.si L195-199`.

**v0.2 canonical ladder update:**

