## 5. Acceptance criteria

(từ v0.1 §5, + 3 item mới v0.2)

1. ✅ 4 interface + union `Moment` pass TypeScript strict
2. ✅ 4 factory function `create*` populate `kind` + `sirasign` auto
3. ✅ `storagePathsFor` exhaustive check compile (no `default:` branch, ESLint enforce)
4. ✅ `computeSirasign` produces deterministic hash (same input → same hash)
5. ✅ Integration test: roundtrip `createScar → persist → query → verify` pass
6. ✅ Scanner check: no plain `{kind: string}` usage, phải dùng typed Moment
7. ✅ No duplicate entries with SuperDictionary.ts (cross-verify script)
8. ✅ **NEW v0.2** — `storagePathsFor` mapping align B.1 §9: SCAR→`.ml`, KHAI→`.na`, GIAC→`.na`+`.obitan`, MOTION→`.na` delta
9. ✅ **NEW v0.2** — Moments position compliance: no direct dispatch qua L1/L2/L3, no cross Bridge v2 (scanner enforce: `src/governance/moments/` forbid import từ `src/core/nauion/resonance/` hoặc `bridge_v2`)
10. ✅ **NEW v0.2** — GIAC_NGO persist atomicity documented (behavior khi 1 target fail — proposal chờ Gatekeeper seal)

