## 9. Open Items — 3 group (NEW v0.2)

### 9.1. Rule đã khóa (seal)

- 4 MomentKind discriminated union: SCAR / KHAI_SANG / GIAC_NGO / MOTION_TICH_CUC
- Factory function contract: auto fill `kind` + `sirasign`, readonly everywhere, immutable records
- **Position Moments trong ontology/runtime axis (Π_system)** — KHÔNG topology (L1/L2/L3), KHÔNG boundary forensics (Bridge v2)
- `sirasign` = SHA-256 canonical JSON (Hiến Pháp v5.0 Điều 7 — no btoa, no obfuscation)
- **Storage mapping per B.1 §9:** SCAR→`.ml` · KHAI→`.na` continuum · GIAC→`.na` + `.obitan` dual · MOTION→`.na` delta
- **GIAC_NGO dual-target** (memory edit continuum + obitan vết hằn)
- Moments reference capability causation chain, KHÔNG orphan moment
- `storagePathsFor` exhaustive switch (TypeScript compile error if case missing)
- ScarClass v0.2 mở rộng: thêm `LAYER_DRIFT` + `RUNTIME_MISMATCH` (derived từ SCAR thực tế phiên 20260423-20260424)
- Moments KHÔNG dispatch qua L1/L2/L3, KHÔNG cross Bridge v2 (scanner enforce import boundary)
- Moments internal governance filesystem only, không qua Mạch HeyNa stream

### 9.2. Parameter chờ calibrate (proposal, depend Phase E data)

- `timestamp_ns` precision floor — chưa có Phase E data confirm
- Heuristic event → region boundary mapping — depend capability registry Phase C (Kim owner)
- **σ window cho moment burst detection** — DRAFT Phase E.7 (Thiên kỷ luật 1: σ=0.5 octave chỉ DRAFT, chưa seal)
- Recurrence threshold (bao nhiêu SCAR cùng pattern → upgrade scar_class severity) — depend Phase E
- Filename `<entity>kh*.na` wildcard resolve pattern — depend Gatekeeper naming convention seal
- `<date>` placeholder format — persister owner pick sau khi seal

### 9.3. Policy chờ Gatekeeper

- **Memory location path:** `src/governance/memory/<entity>/` (current) vs tương lai `memory/<entity>/` root (Q3 self-neoed DEFER, waiting Gatekeeper lock governance structure overall)
- **Persister implementation owner:** Băng `maintain_validators` (v0.1 + v0.2 default) hay Kim `modify_kernel` (nếu persister coupled kernel)?
- **MOTION_TICH_CUC `gatekeeper_witnessed: boolean`** — policy sign-off cần Gatekeeper manual attestation khi `true`, hay trust entity self-report?
- **GIAC_NGO persist atomicity** — khi persist dual target (`.na` + `.obitan`), policy rollback nếu 1 trong 2 fail? All-or-nothing hay best-effort?
- **Cross-persona query RBAC** — persona A có được query moments của persona B không? Scope authority lock cần extend cho query permission?
- **Moment immutability vs amendment** — khi phát hiện moment record SAI (ví dụ attribution v1 → v4 như SCAR-20260424-EP-09), policy fix: ship new moment với `recurrence_of` hay edit in-place? (Current: ship new, không edit — nhưng chưa seal canonical)

